                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                      </svg>
                    </span>
                    <span>La paz es la madre de la sanación</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-start text-gray-800">
                    <span class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-teal-500 flex items-center justify-center mr-3 mt-1 flex-shrink-0">
                      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                      </svg>
                    </span>
                    <span>La alegría es el motor</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-start text-gray-800">
                    <span class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-teal-500 flex items-center justify-center mr-3 mt-1 flex-shrink-0">
                      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                      </svg>
                    </span>
